<script>
    var languageRTL = 'ltr';

    var steplan = 1;
    var marquee = "left";

    if (languageRTL == "rtl") {
        steplan = -1;
        marquee = "right";
    }

    var options = {
        $AutoPlay: false,
        $PauseOnHover: 1,
        $ArrowKeyNavigation: true,
        $SlideWidth: 800,
        $SlideHeight: 450,
        $SlideSpacing: 20,
        $DisplayPieces: 2,
        $ParkingPosition: 185,
        $ArrowNavigatorOptions: {
            $Class: $JssorArrowNavigator$,
            $ChanceToShow: 2,
            $AutoCenter: 2,
            $Steps: steplan,
        }
    };

    var jssor_slider1 = new $JssorSlider$("slider1_container", options);

    $(document).ready(function () {

        $('.homebxslider').bxSlider({
            captions: true,
            auto: true,
            pause: 6000,
            mode: 'fade',
            onSliderLoad: function () {
                console.log("slider bitti");
            }
        });

        $('#choicebxslider').bxSlider({
            captions: true,
            auto: true,
            pause: 4000,
            onSliderLoad: function () {
                $("#EditorIlkFoto").hide();
            }
        });

        $('#choicebxslider2').bxSlider({
            captions: true,
            auto: true,
            pause: 4000,
            onSliderLoad: function () {
                $("#KategoriIlkFoto").hide();
            }
        });



        $('#m1').marquee({
            pauseOnHover: true,
            duration: 18000,
            gap: 50,
            delayBeforeStart: 0,
            direction: marquee,
            duplicated: true
        });

        $('#m2').marquee({
            pauseOnHover: true,
            duration: 18000,
            gap: 50,
            delayBeforeStart: 0,
            direction: marquee,
            duplicated: true
        });

        ScaleSlider();

        $(window).bind("load", ScaleSlider);
        $(window).bind("resize", ScaleSlider);
        $(window).bind("orientationchange", ScaleSlider);

        $(".slidehome").removeClass("slidehome");
        $(".overlay").removeClass("homecaption");
    });

    function ScaleSlider() {
        var parentWidth = jssor_slider1.$Elmt.parentNode.clientWidth;
        if (parentWidth)
            jssor_slider1.$ScaleWidth(Math.min(parentWidth, 1170));
        else
            window.setTimeout(ScaleSlider, 30);
    }
</script>
